history.content:
Dear Students:

Unless you are planning to graduate at the end of Summer 2015, students who intend to serve as a first-time GSI in summer do NOT need to enroll in EE/CS 375 this Spring. If you are hired as first-time GSIs this summer, we will reach out to you with further instructions on how to enroll in your 375 course. 
If you are a first-time GSI, and are planning to graduate at the end of Summer 15, you must take your EE/CS 375 course in Spring 15. 
Please note that the add/drop deadline for Spring 15 is tonight (February 20th) at 11:59 pm, but I encourage you to make any changes to your schedule as early as possible. 
Please let me know if you have questions.
history.subject: ** UPDATE ** Important announcement about EE/CS 375
